data.description: Gorgeous and totally renovated, five bedroom, 3200 square foot North End beach home just a short distance to the oceanfront beaches! Wonderful bright and open floor plan featuring a beautiful all new chefs kitchen, huge family room with cathedral ceiling, gas fireplace and new floors, luxurious first floor primary suite offering a new marble bathroom with heated floors, additional first floor bedroom/office, a second floor primary suite with new bathroom and large walk in closet and a beautifully renovated hall bathroom. SO many updates including a new roof, new skylights, new windows, new two zone, 16+ Seer HVAC, new hot water heater and circulating pump, new floors and staircase, new mudroom and so many more quality updates! This exceptional home has it all!
